              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
            },
            "body": "You should definitely see if you can improve your python script by looking at a static resolution file instead of dynamically pinging DNS at run time. That'll clearly improve your performance.\n\nOverall, we wish to expose this information to AMs from RM itself so that each AM doesn't need to do this itself. That is tracked via YARN-435. If that okay with you, please close this as duplicate.",
